OL,3,CVeteran trapped in flat for months
OL,4,Cbecause of broken lift
OL,6,FAn 82 year old veteran with advanced
OL,7,Flung cancer said he's been trapped in
OL,8,Fhis Southampton flat for more than
OL,9,Ffour months because of a broken lift.
OL,11,FFormer Royal Marine Terry Manley
OL,12,Frelies on a wheelchair and says
OL,13,Fwithout the lift, he's unable to leave
OL,14,Fhis first-floor flat and is fearful of
OL,15,Fmissing vital hospital appointments.
OL,17,F"I need the lift just to go up one
OL,18,Fflight of stairs to get to a car," he
OL,19,Fsaid. "The trouble is, the longer I
OL,20,Fstay here, I start feeling depressed."
