OL,3,CVeteran trapped in flat for months
OL,4,Cbecause of broken lift
OL,6,FThe lift in Terry's social housing
OL,7,Fblock, run by Sanctuary Housing, has
OL,8,Fbeen out of order since June. He said
OL,9,Fproblems with it have been ongoing for
OL,10,Fyears - and that he's even been
OL,11,Ftrapped inside twice, needing
OL,12,Ffirefighters to rescue him.
OL,14,FOther residents, many of them elderly,
OL,15,Fare also affected. Terry relies on his
OL,16,Fpartner and carer Carol to help him.
OL,18,F"We're all old, walking up stairs it's
OL,19,Fjust not on," Carol said. "It's
OL,20,Fdesperately needed. We feel totally
OL,21,Fneglected."
