OL,3,CVeteran trapped in flat for months
OL,4,Cbecause of broken lift
OL,6,FTerry tries to remain helpful, and
OL,7,Fhopes the lift will be fixed in time
OL,8,Ffor him to attend Remembrance Day
OL,9,Fcommemorations with his family.
OL,11,FIn a statement, Sanctuary said they
OL,12,F"understand the difficulties' and are
OL,13,Fdoing all they can to restore the lift
OL,14,Fas soon as possible.
OL,16,F"Our contractor has already attended
OL,17,Fthe site several times. However, this
OL,18,Fis a significant and complex repair
OL,19,Frequiring specialist parts to be
OL,20,Fmanufactured from overseas.
