OL,3,CVeteran trapped in flat for months
OL,4,Cbecause of broken lift
OL,6,F"As soon as the necessary parts are
OL,7,Fmanufactured and shipped, the work to
OL,8,Frestore the lift will be carried out
OL,9,Fas the highest priority.
OL,11,F"We are continuing to offer our
OL,12,Fcustomers any support they need while
OL,13,Fthe lift remains out of service. This
OL,14,Fincludes supporting less mobile
OL,15,Fresidents with laundry, shopping and
OL,16,Fdisposing of refuse. We have also
OL,17,Foffered to temporarily move customers
OL,18,Fwith specific mobility needs where
OL,19,Fthey require further support."
